01:01:22,289 --> 01:01:23,289
Ya.

936
01:01:23,289 --> 01:01:26,320
Sebesar itu keinginanmu menikah?

937
01:01:27,090 --> 01:01:28,130
Ya.

938
01:01:33,500 --> 01:01:34,869
Maka tetaplah bekerja.

